              "type": "story",
              "character": "lila",
              "story": "Lila the Owl loves reading books! She says: 'A sentence is a group of words that makes complete sense.' For example: 'The dog runs fast.' That is a sentence. But 'the dog' alone is NOT a sentence \u2014 it doesn't tell us anything complete!",
