              "character": "lila",
              "story": "Lila has one book. But she wants more! One book \u2192 two BOOKS. One is SINGULAR. More than one is PLURAL. Usually we add -s or -es to make plural. Book \u2192 Books. Box \u2192 Boxes. Watch \u2192 Watches!",
